description:
Where does the left go now? AOC blames moderates for Virginia "bummer," says progressives "weren't really even invited." Microsoft goes full woke: introductions highlighting pronouns, race and hairstyles. Democrats desperately trying to pass the Biden budget. Peter Navarro, former Assistant to President Donald Trump and author of In Trump Time: A Journal of America's Plague Year, calls in to talk about the Biden administration. Navarro discusses the dangers of Dr. Fauci hero worship.
